{"tid":1915731,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"防暴警在秘密警察配合下 於下午制服多名大埔示威者","createTime":"2020-03-08T12:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T17:54:07.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"42e66ea8f845af28b8d368d78cc0725c4615e588","tid":1915731,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T12:06:36.000Z","msg":"防暴警在大埔制服多名堵路示威者<br />\n<br />\n網上有人發起下午在大埔遊行，反對設立指定診所，下午約4時，過百人在安祥路走出馬路，用雜物堵路，防暴警員隨即到場，施放胡椒噴劑，驅趕人群，其後在十字路口，在喬裝警員配合下，制服多人並綁上索帶，亦有長者涉嫌擲水樽，被警員按在地上帶走。<br />\n<br />\n被醫管局列為指定診所、位於大埔汀角路的賽馬會普通科門診診所，遭人噴漆，政府強烈譴責示威者惡意破壞，罔顧市民對公共衞生服務需要，醫管局亦譴責惡意破壞行為，將事件交警方處理，同時加強診所保安。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1272315&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1272315%26csid%3D261_341&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5Bw2vf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=e2dd93db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1272315&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"d29fe466ed2f3a0ddaf5600eb4d21d3a5faef9b0","tid":1915731,"uid":105340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T13:04:53.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"a9b891824816ab3d3523f48018e3bb22c627e155","tid":1915731,"uid":311337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T14:07:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6e33547161bb15f41c6c74ffeba0604f73516fd0","tid":1915731,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T17:54:07.000Z","msg":"黑警未出發先屯兵了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}